es.upv.grc.grcbox.common

Class GrcBoxInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.upv.grc.grcbox.common.GrcBoxInterface

  • public class GrcBoxInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class GrcBoxInterface. This class represents a network interface in the GRCBox server. Currently cost variable is not used.
